6. ✅ Telegram bot integration
7. ✅ Schedule validation rules
8. ✅ Image optimization pipeline

### Phase 3 (Nice to Have)
9. ✅ In-app notification system
10. ✅ Cursor-based pagination
11. ✅ Advanced analytics endpoints

